[
  {
    "page": 1,
    "title": "10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants",
    "article": "\n<p>The price of dental implants might seem daunting. But regardless of your budget, there are many ways to obtain them. We offer you 10 simple ways to help restore your smile.</p>\n<img alt=\"10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants_1\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_1.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_1.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_1.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_1.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 2,
    "title": "10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants",
    "article": "\n<h4>1. Research Prices</h4>\n<img alt=\"10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants_2\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_2.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_2.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_2.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_2.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Before getting dental implants, be sure to shop around. Many dental clinics offer special discounts or payment plans. Online dental forums and review sites can also provide advice on dental implants.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 3,
    "title": "10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants",
    "article": "\n<h4>2. Inquiring About Discounts</h4>\n<img alt=\"10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants_3\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_3.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_3.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_3.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_3.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>You can directly ask the dental clinic if they offer discounts or payment plans. Additionally, some clinics may work with you to create a payment plan for your dental implants.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 4,
    "title": "10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants",
    "article": "\n<h4>3. Dental Insurance</h4>\n<img alt=\"10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants_4\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_4.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_4.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_4.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_4.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Many dental insurance plans cover dental implants. If you have dental insurance, check with your provider.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 5,
    "title": "10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants",
    "article": "\n<h4>4. Dental Savings Plans</h4>\n<img alt=\"10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants_5\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_5.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_5.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_5.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_5.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Dental savings plans allow you to pay a small monthly fee in exchange for discounted dental care services. In this way, you can get dental implants at a more affordable price.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 6,
    "title": "10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants",
    "article": "\n<h4>5. Government Programs</h4>\n<img alt=\"10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants_6\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_6.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_6.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_6.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_6.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Many governments offer plans to help cover the cost of dental implants. Some dental charities also provide financial assistance for implants.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 7,
    "title": "10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants",
    "article": "\n<h4>6. Inquiring About Interest-Free Financing</h4>\n<img alt=\"10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants_7\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_7.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_7.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_7.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_7.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Many dental clinics offer special financing plans that can make dental implants more affordable.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 8,
    "title": "10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants",
    "article": "\n<h4>7. Crowdfunding</h4>\n<img alt=\"10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants_8\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_8.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_8.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_8.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_8.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>If you can't afford the costs yourself, you can raise donations for dental implant expenses through websites like GoFundMe and Fundly. This is also a great way to obtain dental implants.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 9,
    "title": "10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants",
    "article": "\n<h4>8. Asking About Grants</h4>\n<img alt=\"10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants_9\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_9.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_9.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_9.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_9.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Many dental implant providers offer grants or scholarships to help cover the cost of implants. These grants are usually awarded based on financial need. You can contact local dental implant providers to inquire about available grants.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 10,
    "title": "10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants",
    "article": "\n<h4>9. Other Options</h4>\n<img alt=\"10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants_10\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_10.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_10.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_10.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_10.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>If dental implants aren't suitable for you, you can consider dentures and bridges, or opt for cosmetic bonding or veneers.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 11,
    "title": "10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants",
    "article": "\n<h4>10. Take Good Care Of Your Teeth</h4>\n<img alt=\"10 Must-See Ways To Easily Get Dental Implants_11\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_11.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_11.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_11.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants/10-must-see-ways-to-easily-get-dental-implants_11.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Remember, it's crucial to maintain proper dental care even after getting implants. Good oral hygiene and regular dental check-ups are essential for the health of your implants.</p>\n</img>"
  }
]